i woke up

and felt so unhappy

when im in a relationship i put my feelings in hiding. I dont tell that person how i really feel about anything. I let them spill their guts but i have nothing in return. The only time i can show emotion is when im pissed. So when im mad i can cuss them out and say all these hurtful things but when im really inlove with them and cant get enough, i dont say a word. And i dont show if something hurts my feelings, its like against my own personal law to let a boy see me cry i cant let them see they they have won. I dont want ne guy to know that they have ne control over my emotions. And the leading to all of this is Dennis Falcon. YEP man of the year. He has hurt me more then ne one has ever hurt me before. And he has totally proven to me that not one man in this world is worth trusting or even falling inlove. I love scott, dont get me wrong, but its going to take a LONG time for me to actually let him in and see the person i truly am. I treat him so badly at times, and i feel awful but im not one to admit im wrong and apologize i play the tough guy and try to win every battle and if i lose im pissed. I really need to talk to someone and learn how to let these issues go. I need to see how i can get rid of this anger and hurt i have inside of me. This isnt fair to scott. Me being totally incapable of putting my gaurd down.

The most recent argument we had was because of another girl texting him and i was under the impression that he was talking to her in an intimate way (which doesnt mean sexual) and because i was so scared he was talking to another woman in such a way i literally freaked out. I cried so hard i couldnt breathe, i yelled and screamed at him,i acted a total fool...and for what? Because i let past experiences take over my brain and i made an assumption that Scott was going to hurt me the same way Dennis did. But why would he do that? Scott is so inlove me with its unreal, he would NEVER do anything like that to me. BUT because it has happened in the psat and caused so much damage to my heart and soul i felt as if it could happen again. I Have to realize IM NOT WITH DENNIS, im with someone who loves me.

EASIER SAID THAN DONE

i seriously need to stop.

i need to stop worrying all the time about everything. I need to think postive more often and stop looking at the negative aspect of things. I think thats why i get in such a bad mood sometimes cause im always stressing about things. I always feel like everything i do isnt good enough, and i was thinking about all of this last night and i think i feel that way because i was brough up that way. i was always told i could do better and i never got a pat on the back or "good job" when i was younger. It was always someone yelling at me telling me i wasnt good enough or verbally abusing me for everything i did. And i think my mom needs to stay out of my business now. Im 19 years old i dont need her dictating everything i do and telling me i cant do things because she doesnt like it. Thats why i need to move out. I need to able to make decisions on my own and now have to butt heads with her about every little mistake i make or if i make a decision she doesnt agree with. This is the point in my life where really i need to think about ME and what I want. Like yesterday i had no concerns with scott other then he didnt trust me and thats it. and then my mom gets home and tells me this and that and then i have things in my head that arent supposed to be there and i get all frusterated and i cry and then i say things to him and it just doesnt turn out good we almost broke up and for wat.... because my mom filled my head with bull shit. I just really need to think about how i am going to go about talking with her about how i need to be able to make my own decsions and just for her to back up and step in only if im going to get hurt or get introuble. I just need to do things on my own.

wow it felt good to atleast write all this down. i feel a lot better now <3
